{
  "title": "About Family Plugin",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "be5122a8320d633c",
      "text": "This plugin, type: **family**, gathers families of related wiki sites and adds them to your neighborhood. It augments the Present plugin: instead of only listing sister sites, you choose *which* families to gather."
    },
    {
      "type": "family",
      "id": "01b9d66d009aa2c7",
      "text": "FAMILY"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "625ddc4e896c6e27",
      "text": "Write one **command** per line (UPPERCASE, an optional trailing colon ‚Äî see the [[Fedwiki DSL Skill]] convention):\n\n- `FAMILY` ‚Äî `PARENT` and `SISTERS` together (shorthand)\n- `SISTERS` ‚Äî sibling sites sharing the parent domain\n- `PARENT` ‚Äî the parent-domain site itself\n- `CHILDREN` ‚Äî sub-domains of this site\n- `FARM` ‚Äî every wiki in the farm\n- `NEIGHBOURHOOD` ‚Äî the sites currently in your neighborhood\n- `SNAPSHOT` ‚Äî freeze the current neighborhood *(same as NEIGHBOURHOOD)*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "cedff82dadcf82fd",
      "text": "Each gathered site is registered as a neighbor, so its pages join your search and lineage. The page still reads normally without the plugin."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "47fd6339cb39a685",
      "text": "## Repositories\n\n- **GitHub**: [Hitchhikers-Guide-to-the-Galaxy/wiki-plugin-family](https://github.com/Hitchhikers-Guide-to-the-Galaxy/wiki-plugin-family)\n- **npm**: [wiki-plugin-family](https://www.npmjs.com/package/wiki-plugin-family) ‚Äî `npm install wiki-plugin-family`"
    }
  ],
